----------------
Just below the Jakobshorn peak on a rocky NW slope. Snow depth below average for this elevation and aspect. Performed PST tests with a prototype accelerometer to see what it will record. Also recorded high-speed PTV movies.

PROFILE
-------
The new snow from the last 10 days has some crusts in it and is sitting on the sahara layer @ 51. Then a relatively thick variable refrozen layer with multiple crusts and percolation fingers. The base still consists of very well perserved depth hoar.

RUTSCHBLOCK
-----------
No Rutschblock. ECT propagated well on the depth hoar. Performed 3 PSTs @ 14 and @ 22:
PST 40 SF @ 22
PST 35 END/120 @ 14

SNOW SURFACE
------------
Surface hoar

RUTSCHBLOCK TEST
----------------
Layer@14.0: ECT 21/21</slf:text></slf:profiletext></slf:profiletext-list></caaml:customData></caaml:metaData><caaml:timeRef><caaml:recordTime><caaml:TimeInstant><caaml:timePosition>2016-04-29T10:00:00+02:00</caaml:timePosition></caaml:TimeInstant></caaml:recordTime><caaml:dateTimeReport>2016-04-29T14:54:31+02:00</caaml:dateTimeReport><caaml:dateTimeLastEdit>2016-04-29T15:11:48+02:00</caaml:dateTimeLastEdit></caaml:timeRef><caaml:srcRef/><caaml:locRef><caaml:name>Davos - Jakobshorn - Gipfel</caaml:name><caaml:validElevation><caaml:ElevationPosition uom="m"><caaml:position>2580</caaml:position></caaml:ElevationPosition></caaml:validElevation><caaml:validAspect><caaml:AspectPosition><caaml:position>NW</caaml:position></caaml:AspectPosition></caaml:validAspect><caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:SlopeAnglePosition uom="deg"><caaml:position>34</caaml:position></caaml:SlopeAnglePosition></caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:pointLocation><gml:Point id="pointID" srsName="urn:ogc:def:crs:OGC:1.3:CRS84" srsDimension="2"><gml:pos>9.849376 46.772596</gml:pos></gml:Point></caaml:pointLocation></caaml:locRef><caaml:snowProfileResultsOf><caaml:SnowProfileMeasurements dir="top down"><caaml:profileDepth uom="cm">67.0</caaml:profileDepth><caaml:weatherCond><caaml:airTempPres uom="degC">-7.0</caaml:airTempPres></caaml:weatherCond><caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:hS><caaml:Components><caaml:height uom="cm">67.0</caaml:height></caaml:Components></caaml:hS></caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:stratProfile><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">0.0</caaml:depthTop><caaml:thickness uom="cm">0.3</caaml:thickness><caaml:wetness uom="">D</caaml:wetness><caaml:grainFormPrimary>SH</caaml:grainFormPrimary><caaml:grainSize uom="mm"><caaml:Components><caaml:avg>2.0</caaml:avg><caaml:avgMax>3.0</caaml:avgMax></caaml:Components></caaml:grainSize><caaml:hardness uom="">F</caaml:hardness></caaml:Layer><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">0.29999999999999716</caaml:depthTop><caaml:thickness uom="cm">1.7</caaml:thickness><caaml:w